# agent_logs — persistent TDD/orchestrator checkpoints and structured artifacts
#
# Per the TDD workflow (see .grok/docs/tdd-workflow.md and AGENTS.md):
#   agent_logs/<feature-slug-or-run-id>/
#     - tdd-plan.json
#     - checkpoint-*.md
#     - coverage-report.json
#     - *.diff
#     - state.json
#
# These are working artifacts. You may gitignore the directory or commit selected runs.
# The orchestrator and sub-agents are instructed to read from here for scoped context.
